OL,6,FA man who murdered his partner by
OL,7,Frepeatedly slamming her head on the
OL,8,Ffloor on their first anniversary has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for life.
OL,11,FKain Tailby attacked Christine Everett-
OL,12,FHickson, known as Chrissie, in the
OL,13,Fkitchen of their flat in Riddings in
OL,14,FDerbyshire after a night out, three
OL,15,Fdays after Valentine's Day in 2024.
