OL,3,CMan who murdered partner on their
OL,4,Cfirst anniversary jailed for life
OL,6,FThe pair were arguing. Tailby, 31,
OL,7,Fdescribed it as some "pushing and
OL,8,Fshoving". He pinned the 21-year-old to
OL,9,Fthe ground before grabbing her by the
OL,10,Fneck and hitting her head on the floor
OL,11,Fa number of times.
OL,13,FA neighbour described how he heard
OL,14,Fseveral loud bangs before silence.
OL,16,FTailby then called 999 asking for
OL,17,Fpolice and the ambulance service. He
OL,18,Ftried to downplay his actions,
OL,19,Fclaiming Chrissie was the instigator
OL,20,Fof the "pushing and shoving".
