OL,3,CMan who murdered partner on their
OL,4,Cfirst anniversary jailed for life
OL,6,FHe told the operator Chrissie was in
OL,7,Fthe bath, bleeding from her ear and he
OL,8,Fhad been trying to clean up the blood.
OL,10,FChrissie was rushed to hospital where
OL,11,Fdoctors discovered she had skull
OL,12,Ffractures and a traumatic brain
OL,13,Finjury. The 21-year-old died five days
OL,14,Flater.
OL,16,FTailby was arrested at the scene and
OL,17,Fin interview told officers various
OL,18,Fstories about what had happened that
OL,19,Fnight.,
