OL,3,CMan who murdered partner on their
OL,4,Cfirst anniversary jailed for life
OL,6,FThe 31-year-old, of Greenhill Lane,
OL,7,FRiddings, admitted manslaughter but
OL,8,Fdenied murdering Chrissie.
OL,10,FHe was found guilty of murder by a
OL,11,Fjury after a trial at Derby Crown
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FHe has been jailed for life, and must
OL,15,Fserve a minimum of 16 years and 329
OL,16,Fdays before he can be considered for
OL,17,Frelease.
