OL,3,CMan who murdered partner on their
OL,4,Cfirst anniversary jailed for life
OL,6,FSentencing him, Judge Shaun Smith KC,
OL,7,Fsaid: "In just a few minutes in your
OL,8,Fflat, your explosion of anger and
OL,9,Fviolence snuffed out the life of
OL,10,FChrissie.
OL,12,F"She was just 21 when she died five
OL,13,Fdays later. She was described by her
OL,14,Fmum in her victim impact statement as
OL,15,F"vibrant, funny, innocent, truly
OL,16,Fbeautiful, compassionate, compelling.
OL,17,FA young lady who had just begun to
OL,18,Flive.
