OL,3,CMan who murdered partner on their
OL,4,Cfirst anniversary jailed for life
OL,6,F"Your life and the lives of so many
OL,7,Fothers, have been permanently changed
OL,8,Fforever by your violence. Why? Only
OL,9,Fyou will truly know. Whatever the
OL,10,Freason, it was no justification for
OL,11,Fthe level of violence you used. The
OL,12,Feffect of your actions on those who
OL,13,Fknew and loved Chrissie has been, and
OL,14,Fwill remain, immeasurable.
OL,16,F"Her life and smile were infectious,
OL,17,Fshe was kind and considerate. That
OL,18,FChrissie's mum forgives you is beyond
OL,19,Fadmirable. (But) I accept you are not
OL,20,Fan evil man."
